{"tid":2255052,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新片警暴劇情似港現況","createTime":"2020-10-23T08:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T10:20:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"625a14b6a41435e6fd9c6b88df7f50ac321dc317","tid":2255052,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201023/U4BOPM2Z7RFQ7DE6CNJ7D5GPJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201023%2FU4BOPM2Z7RFQ7DE6CNJ7D5GPJ4%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=55874dcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201023%2FU4BOPM2Z7RFQ7DE6CNJ7D5GPJ4%2F&h=70c792d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201023/U4BOPM2Z7RFQ7DE6CNJ7D5GPJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新片警暴劇情似港現況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/S8XnZsE7No4xmn7AeGpr-U_k_88=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7YFLCVSDWVGSVELIZGLCJGKLRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FS8XnZsE7No4xmn7AeGpr-U_k_88%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7YFLCVSDWVGSVELIZGLCJGKLRY.jpg&h=e2c6bf48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《芝加哥七人案：驚世審判》中有不少警察施放催淚彈及追打示威者場面，不禁令人聯想到去年香港反送中抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n力撐港人的祖瑟夫哥頓利域一直活躍於荷李活影壇，上周於Netflix上架的新作《芝加哥七人案：驚世審判》（The Trial of the Chicago 7），竟湊巧有示威抗爭與警暴內容。電影講述60年代美國的一場政治審判，當中講及示威者抗爭與被捕情況，例如警察包圍公路阻撓示威者離開、對手無寸鐵的示威者大放催淚彈及棍襲等，跟香港上年反送中場面不謀而合。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【童星拍劇】憑《心跳500天》蜚聲國際<br />\n<br />\n該片由憑《社交網絡》（The Social Network）奧斯卡最佳編劇的Aaron Sorkin自編自導，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n1968年美國反越戰浪潮不絕，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pdxSJtO2IO07gUBZIONOtU-RugM=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UZHZRG43YFCDDAXN6IA7HXJOMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpdxSJtO2IO07gUBZIONOtU-RugM%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUZHZRG43YFCDDAXN6IA7HXJOMA.jpg&h=fdb69bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■祖瑟夫於戲中扮演檢察官，表面跟抗爭者對立，但卻恪守法律公正原則。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XmPJuxWYPS_AXLzNtaUNhlRwLNI=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/U2TKNNPZ5REAJHMWPXSXCEPILQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXmPJuxWYPS_AXLzNtaUNhlRwLNI%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FU2TKNNPZ5REAJHMWPXSXCEPILQ.jpg&h=8b824889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《芝加哥七人案：驚世審判》講述當年反越戰示威掀起激烈的警民衝突，一眾示威人士被控叛亂罪。"},{"pid":"167e7e90a51d279c8019070ca4e8657cc732a98a","tid":2255052,"uid":157092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zRe5bWw0FZI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzRe5bWw0FZI&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=92d5dbf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zRe5bWw0FZI</a>"}]}